# NCF Trust Chain Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Constitution[NCF Constitution]
    RegistryAuthority[Nexus Registry Authority]
    CertificationAuthority[Certification Authority]
    Namespace[Organization Namespace]
    Organization[Organization]
    Workforce[Workforce]
    Agent[Agent]
    Workflow[Workflow]
    Run[Workflow Run]
    Asset[Asset]
    Metric[Metric]

    Constitution --> RegistryAuthority
    RegistryAuthority --> CertificationAuthority
    RegistryAuthority --> Namespace
    Namespace --> Organization
    Organization --> Workforce
    Workforce --> Agent
    Agent --> Workflow
    Workflow --> Run
    Run --> Asset
    Asset --> Metric
```
